{"tid":1614070,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"應該俾個機會美心跪","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T14:10:02.000Z","uid":269125,"like":107,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"20a05aea4e3205be850f4c2f46bd242c62fbafeb","tid":1614070,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:37:22.000Z","msg":"首先講明我唔係想批評爆元氣/Starbucks，或者唔應該針對美心<br />\n而係理性討論搞美心其實傷唔傷到伍淑清<br />\n<br />\n而我既結論係，其實向美心施壓對伍淑清有啲不痛不痒<br />\n<br />\n原因請睇呢篇報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_696959_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_696959_0&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7GVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=9debc3ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_696959_0&h=d1a04089\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_696959_0</a><br />\n<br />\n伍淑清只係得100股，然後佢被大房打壓<br />\n雖然美心都係奶共架啦，但畢竟佢地都未出賣手足<br />\n我地應該俾個機會伍家大房<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一係就出篇聲明譴責伍淑清</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一係買晒佢個100股以示同佢割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家應該俾個機會美心跪，雖然美心一跪內地盤數就爆硬<br />\n不過買晒佢個100股叫做低調啲，等你有啲渣拿<br />\n伍家，諗下點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c08f3d03b6ff388be4115e1dc697cfc520deb1","tid":1614070,"uid":38904,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n始終美心未至於出賣手足<br />\n<br />\n佢唔跪底再裝修都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd97a3a95fa09e3c91cc9a7ccd6d4b00c6cf87a","tid":1614070,"uid":997,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:42:20.000Z","msg":"叫美心公開出聲明譴責條八婆先"},{"pid":"8f3a75edbdc0d6ec3b66208cb5ce792c13317e95","tid":1614070,"uid":288707,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:43:26.000Z","msg":